@baseUrl = https://localhost:60711

### Analyze — single sentence
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Ner/Analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sentences": ["Microsoft was founded by Bill Gates in Seattle"]
}

### Analyze — two sentences
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Ner/Analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sentences": [
    "Microsoft was founded by Bill Gates in Seattle",
    "Elon Musk announced Tesla would open a factory in Berlin"
  ]
}

### Analyze — only named entities expected
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Ner/Analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sentences": [
    "Barack Obama served as the 44th President of the United States",
    "Google acquired YouTube for over a billion dollars",
    "Paris and London are popular European destinations"
  ]
}

### Validation — empty sentence list (expects 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Ner/Analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sentences": []
}
